                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12521771" author="fmeschbe" created="Wed, 22 Aug 2007 12:54:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Refactored how events are fired: Now the PID and Factory PID for the Event are given as parameters and not as ConfigurationImpl object which in fact may be null in case of a non-existing configuration for a newly registered ManagedService.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fixed in Rev. 568514.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12521772" author="fmeschbe" created="Wed, 22 Aug 2007 12:55:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;And deployed new bundle.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So I mark this resolved.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12521829" author="fmeschbe" created="Wed, 22 Aug 2007 15:32:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Tom confirmed the fix to be good. Hence closing this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
